      "text": "爱笑的眼睛",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 7.49,
      "time_str": "00:07.490",
      "text": "演唱：林俊杰",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 14.64,
      "time_str": "00:14.640",
      "text": "如果不是那镜子",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 16.73,
      "time_str": "00:16.730",
      "text": "不像你不藏秘密",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 21.26,
      "time_str": "00:21.260",
      "text": "我还不肯相信",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 23.02,
      "time_str": "00:23.020",
      "text": "没有你我的笑更美丽",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 28.99,
      "time_str": "00:28.990",
      "text": "那天听你在电话里略带抱歉的关心",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 36.03,
      "time_str": "00:36.030",
      "text": "我嘟的一声切的比你说分手彻底",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 43.5,
      "time_str": "00:43.500",
      "text": "泪湿的衣洗干净阳光里晒干回忆",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 50.18,
      "time_str": "00:50.180",
      "text": "折好了伤心明天起只和快乐出去",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 57.71,
      "time_str": "00:57.710",
      "text": "这爱的城市虽然拥挤",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 61.15,
      "time_str": "01:01.150",
      "text": "如果真的遇见你",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 64.9,
      "time_str": "01:04.900",
      "text": "你不必讶异我的笑她无法代替",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 72.36,
      "time_str": "01:12.360",
      "text": "离开你我才发现自己",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 75.56,
      "time_str": "01:15.560",
      "text": "那爱笑的眼睛流过泪",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 80.23,
      "time_str": "01:20.230",
      "text": "像躲不过的暴风雨",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 83.95,
      "time_str": "01:23.950",
      "text": "淋湿的昨天删去",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 86.81,
      "time_str": "01:26.810",
      "text": "离开你我才找回自己",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 89.95,
      "time_str": "01:29.950",
      "text": "那爱笑的眼睛再见爱情",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 94.69,
      "time_str": "01:34.690",
      "text": "我一定让自己让自己决定",
      "translation": null
    },
